  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>Tons to unpack here, I'm not all the way through but this is exactly the kind of engineering I'm interested in.</html:p>
    <html:p>I'm really curious about eliminators, and general DTT programming.</html:p>
    <html:p>Interesting ideas on avoiding typeclasses as well.</html:p>
    <html:p>But what does HoTT really give you here, I'm confused why he needs the envisioned prover to be HoTT.</html:p>
